I was reminded of the gravity of
the crime I committed.

916
01:13:25,140 --> 01:13:28,820
(Kogetsuan) I want to bring Nao-chan
back to the place I took her from.

917
01:13:29,420 --> 01:13:32,680
That's for Yuriko-san and you.

918
01:13:32,680 --> 01:13:35,120
I thought it was the least
I could do to redeem myself.

919
01:13:35,800 --> 01:13:37,080
To do so,

920
01:13:39,240 --> 01:13:41,620
I have to kick this woman out.

921
01:13:42,200 --> 01:13:45,620
That's why you arranged for Nao arranged
to take over Kougetsuan?

922
01:13:47,020 --> 01:13:50,400
You sent the prank emails to her old work place.

923
01:13:50,440 --> 01:13:52,340
(Hanaoka Nao's mom is a killer)
You're the one who got her sacked, aren't you?

924
01:13:54,310 --> 01:13:57,100
You also asked Yuko-san
to pretend to be her mom.

925
01:13:57,200 --> 01:13:58,680
And you asked the newspaper reporter

926
01:13:58,680 --> 01:14:00,910
to look into the case.

927
01:14:01,110 --> 01:14:01,740
It's all you.

928
01:14:01,740 --> 01:14:03,060
That's right!

929
01:14:04,820 --> 01:14:06,600
I've always wanted to

930
01:14:10,250 --> 01:14:12,650
