But I still don't feel any better.

932
01:14:20,450 --> 01:14:26,310
When all is said and done,
you're still trying to bully her.

933
01:14:30,000 --> 01:14:31,700
If you don't leave,

934
01:14:34,970 --> 01:14:36,280
I'm going to make you disappear.

935
01:14:37,310 --> 01:14:38,480
Stop!

936
