938
01:14:49,680 --> 01:14:51,540
Oh....

939
01:14:53,280 --> 01:14:55,050
It's finally over.

940
01:14:56,170 --> 01:14:57,080
I hate it...

941
01:14:58,480 --> 01:15:00,710
Stop it! Stop it, Takigawa-san!

942
01:15:00,710 --> 01:15:01,880
Why?

943
01:15:03,250 --> 01:15:05,680
You hate this woman, too, don't you?

944
01:15:06,580 --> 01:15:07,940
I hate her.

945
01:15:08,800 --> 01:15:10,420
But she is also...

946
01:15:14,140 --> 01:15:16,740
Tsubaki's mom.

947
01:15:29,340 --> 01:15:30,560
Stop it!

948
01:15:30,560 --> 01:15:31,640
You're covering for me too!

949
