take anyone else you love away from us.

953
01:17:14,020 --> 01:17:15,120
I will

954
01:17:16,450 --> 01:17:19,140
never forgive you, Takigawa-san.

955
01:17:21,560 --> 01:17:25,340
But if you hadn't told us the truth.

956
01:17:27,910 --> 01:17:29,570
I would still have hated this same Kougetsuan.

957
01:17:32,770 --> 01:17:35,020
The shop that my father and mom loved.

958
01:17:37,080 --> 01:17:38,880
I would still have

959
01:17:42,680 --> 01:17:48,220
countinued to hate Tsubaki, too.

960
01:17:52,820 --> 01:17:55,540
You're finally free from the curse.

961
01:18:00,250 --> 01:18:01,400
I...

962
01:18:06,910 --> 01:18:09,280
I wanted to make you happy.

963
01:18:11,680 --> 01:18:12,820
Nao-chan.

964
01:18:17,370 --> 01:18:18,760
Sorry.

965
01:18:55,770 --> 01:18:57,320
It's a very important hand.

966
01:19:00,710 --> 01:19:03,300
I'm fine, thanks.

967
01:19:12,310 --> 01:19:15,740
Tsubaki, I think
you're even more blind than before.

968
01:19:16,850 --> 01:19:19,400
If so, it doesn't matter anymore.

969
01:19:19,510 --> 01:19:21,620
Please hurry up and heal them.

970
01:19:21,740 --> 01:19:24,620
If it's too late, why did I even take over...

971
01:19:33,280 --> 01:19:36,380
What we've been trying so hard to protect.

972
01:19:37,420 --> 01:19:39,300
What was it all about?

973
01:19:41,080 --> 01:19:44,480
If you don't get caught up in the signs
and traditions of Kougetsuan,

974
01:19:45,600 --> 01:19:48,540
maybe the landlady was not the same as now.

975
01:19:49,400 --> 01:19:50,280
The landlady?

976
01:20:00,280 --> 01:20:02,900
It's over.

977
01:20:04,200 --> 01:20:05,240
All.

