981
01:20:45,360 --> 01:20:48,180
Mom, please join in.

982
01:20:48,220 --> 01:20:51,760
â™ªBroken.â™ª

983
01:20:53,680 --> 01:20:57,020
â™ªIt's gone.â™ª

