01:21:02,250 --> 01:21:03,340
Tsubaki-san,

985
01:21:05,050 --> 01:21:06,880
it's time to practice!

986
01:21:08,360 --> 01:21:09,860
Stay with me.

987
01:21:11,170 --> 01:21:14,620
If they don't recognise you as
the successor of Kougetsuan.

988
01:21:14,970 --> 01:21:17,880
You're going to be kicked out of here.

989
01:21:21,420 --> 01:21:22,100
Yes.

990
01:21:39,110 --> 01:21:43,840
We were finally a real family...

991
01:22:13,220 --> 01:22:15,080
Tsubaki.

992
