(The Intensive Care Unit 2nd ICU)

993
01:23:13,680 --> 01:23:16,040
Are you... her son?

994
01:23:18,880 --> 01:23:21,680
It was already too late by the time she arrived.

995
01:23:22,740 --> 01:23:26,400
She had just passed away moments ago.

996
01:23:34,080 --> 01:23:35,110
Takatsuki-san.

997
01:23:38,080 --> 01:23:39,720
Organ donor?

998
01:23:39,720 --> 01:23:40,340
Yes.

999
01:23:40,770 --> 01:23:45,220
She has recently signed up
to be an organ donor, and

1000
01:23:46,370 --> 01:23:48,420
she left a will for the organs

1001
