In order to transplant the cornea,

1013
01:24:24,970 --> 01:24:28,340
it should be removed at the latest
within 24 hours of cardiac arrest....

1014
01:24:36,540 --> 01:24:39,200
Taking over Kougetsuan.

1015
01:24:40,400 --> 01:24:42,820
was the biggest revenge you wanted.

1016
01:24:46,060 --> 01:24:50,740
But... that will never happen anymore.

1017
01:24:52,220 --> 01:24:56,960
I bet you never
cared about what happens to my eye.

1018
01:24:59,370 --> 01:25:00,450
Wait, Tsubaki.

1019
01:25:00,450 --> 01:25:04,940
Tsubaki-san,
this is not about Kougetsuan... or revenge.

1020
01:25:06,680 --> 01:25:08,310
The landlady at that time was...

1021
