Mom.

1028
01:27:14,220 --> 01:27:15,800
So you did it all for me?

1029
01:27:17,850 --> 01:27:19,850
You became the master of Kougetsuan,

1030
01:27:21,850 --> 01:27:24,060
so that I could get my eye surgery done.

1031
01:27:26,680 --> 01:27:28,370
That day 18 years ago,

1032
01:27:31,200 --> 01:27:33,510
I took everything from you.

1033
01:27:40,050 --> 01:27:40,920
Nao.

1034
01:27:43,000 --> 01:27:43,850
Sorry.

1035
01:27:48,420 --> 01:27:51,710
The person who taught me
the joy of making sweets was...

1036
01:27:53,510 --> 01:27:54,600
That was Tsubaki.

1037
01:27:58,880 --> 01:28:01,370
I want to keep making sweets.

1038
01:28:03,140 --> 01:28:07,620
I want Tsubaki to make sweets
that only you can make.

1039
01:28:08,620 --> 01:28:12,360
Freely, from your heart.

1040
01:28:15,650 --> 01:28:18,080
I promise I will protect Kougetsuan.

1041
01:28:25,280 --> 01:28:29,340
You haven't changed at all.

1042
01:28:35,110 --> 01:28:36,360
I'll make it.

1043
01:28:39,370 --> 01:28:41,600
I'll make my own signature sweets.

1044
01:28:51,910 --> 01:28:52,800
Nao.

1045
01:28:59,050 --> 01:29:00,140
Nothing.

1046
01:29:04,820 --> 01:29:09,760
Good luck on your surgery.

1047
01:29:11,820 --> 01:29:12,640
Thanks.

