01:29:41,510 --> 01:29:42,850
Good morning.

1051
01:29:43,560 --> 01:29:45,570
Yamaguchi-san, please make

1052
01:29:45,570 --> 01:29:46,680
the matcha tea dough today.

1053
01:29:46,740 --> 01:29:47,110
Yes.

1054
01:29:47,370 --> 01:29:49,540
Nao-san. Please check the bean paste.

1055
01:29:49,710 --> 01:29:50,480
Yes.

1056
01:29:50,650 --> 01:29:51,940
Um, Nao-san.

1057
01:29:52,200 --> 01:29:54,910
What would you like to put at the front of
today's confectionery?

1058
01:29:55,050 --> 01:29:58,050
Today's specialty will be...

1059
01:29:59,220 --> 01:30:02,440
The peony and the daffodil.
How pretty.

1060
01:30:04,620 --> 01:30:07,200
Every decision I make will be tested.

1061
01:30:07,940 --> 01:30:11,020
(Kogetsuan)
Tsubaki had carried this burden for so long.

1062
01:30:11,370 --> 01:30:15,310
Please don't let Kougetsuan go under.

1063
01:30:17,000 --> 01:30:19,140
I think I'll have some green dango today.

1064
01:30:19,250 --> 01:30:21,140
Yes, I understand.

1065
01:30:21,650 --> 01:30:23,750
And please bring me some Kogetsu monaka as usual.

1066
01:30:23,750 --> 01:30:25,510
