Absolute peace of mind.

1075
01:30:51,420 --> 01:30:55,200
That's what this old shop is all about.

1076
01:30:56,050 --> 01:30:59,020
I've been protecting it for a long time.

1077
01:30:59,800 --> 01:31:03,170
For an unimaginably long time.

1078
01:31:41,000 --> 01:31:42,940
