1084
01:32:04,910 --> 01:32:06,140
Thank you very much!

1085
01:32:06,140 --> 01:32:09,860
I told you I don't like trouble!

1086
01:32:17,680 --> 01:32:18,620
Nao-san.

1087
01:32:19,510 --> 01:32:21,060
Can you come when you're free?

1088
01:32:28,940 --> 01:32:30,020
How is it?

1089
01:32:31,710 --> 01:32:33,420
Jojima-kun. It's great.

1090
01:32:33,710 --> 01:32:36,570
Perfect, isn't it. the Shimaya's warabi mochi.

1091
01:32:37,650 --> 01:32:38,800
Thank you very much.

1092
01:32:39,140 --> 01:32:41,970
I've been able to pay off the debts of
the shop that I had to shoulder.

1093
01:32:42,370 --> 01:32:44,710
I'm thinking of reopening Shimaya.

1094
01:32:48,450 --> 01:32:49,850
Oh, let me help you.

1095
01:32:49,850 --> 01:32:52,310
I'm okay.

1096
01:32:52,310 --> 01:32:54,660
I can't always ask you to help me.

1097
01:32:55,620 --> 01:32:56,910
That's commendable.

1098
01:32:58,400 --> 01:33:02,220
Then can you help me instead this time?

1099
01:33:02,420 --> 01:33:03,820
It's a small shop but

1100
01:33:03,820 --> 01:33:07,200
I'll do my best to get you one of my employees.

1101
01:33:08,340 --> 01:33:11,370
Yes, I'll do my best.

1102
01:33:11,770 --> 01:33:15,110
She's not an employee, she's the landlady!

1103
01:33:15,110 --> 01:33:15,820
What?

1104
01:33:22,500 --> 01:33:25,480
Osugi... he's been through a lot in his own way.

1105
01:33:26,620 --> 01:33:28,120
Shiori-san.

1106
01:33:28,450 --> 01:33:31,280
You should be absolutely happy.

1107
01:33:33,250 --> 01:33:34,140
Yes.

1108
01:33:38,880 --> 01:33:39,880
Nao-san,

1109
01:33:41,170 --> 01:33:43,480
Tsubaki is getting discharged today, isn't he?

1110
01:33:45,050 --> 01:33:48,800
Will Tsubaki-san ever come back to the shop?

1111
01:33:48,800 --> 01:33:50,800
If he comes back here,

1112
01:33:51,480 --> 01:33:53,220
it means he will have to work for Nao-san.

1113
01:33:54,420 --> 01:33:56,110
It's not an easy thing to do.

1114
01:33:56,510 --> 01:33:59,020
Then... where will he go?

1115
01:34:14,860 --> 01:34:16,860
Ah! Sakura!

1116
01:34:17,020 --> 01:34:20,370
It's a spring name like mine.

1117
01:34:21,940 --> 01:34:23,880
Yes, let's make sweets.

1118
01:34:24,080 --> 01:34:27,680
Can I still make sweets here when I grow up?

1119
01:34:27,970 --> 01:34:28,740
Uhm.

1120
01:34:29,280 --> 01:34:33,650
I'll always be with Tsubaki..

1121
01:34:38,970 --> 01:34:43,510
Hey, would you like to marry me?

1122
01:34:52,110 --> 01:34:54,480
I'm going to marry this person.

1123
01:34:56,450 --> 01:35:00,420
Let's try it.
Acting like a married couple.

1124
01:35:00,770 --> 01:35:02,940
You overcome any obstacles
that stand in your way.

1125
01:35:03,140 --> 01:35:06,940
That's the kind of woman I'm in love with.

1126
01:35:12,850 --> 01:35:13,850
Nao.

1127
01:35:14,650 --> 01:35:15,910
Nao.

1128
01:35:16,800 --> 01:35:18,250
Nao.

1129
01:35:51,820 --> 01:35:53,200
Tsubaki, how was your surgery?

1130
01:35:54,800 --> 01:35:56,400
It went well.

1131
01:35:57,000 --> 01:36:01,420
I'm glad. I'm really glad.

1132
01:36:02,570 --> 01:36:04,300
Is that what you want to know?

1133
01:36:11,140 --> 01:36:12,910
Come back to Kougetsuan.

1134
01:36:14,420 --> 01:36:15,760
Kougetsuan needs...

1135
01:36:18,650 --> 01:36:22,340
I need you, Tsubaki.

1136
01:36:25,450 --> 01:36:26,940
No matter how much I hated you,

1137
01:36:28,080 --> 01:36:29,420
how much we hurt each other,

1138
01:36:31,310 --> 01:36:33,170
I couldn't forget you.

1139
01:36:35,420 --> 01:36:37,220
Ever since the day we first met,

1140
01:36:39,140 --> 01:36:40,650
I've been...

1141
01:36:43,850 --> 01:36:45,250
Tsubaki.

1142
01:36:47,800 --> 01:36:49,770
loving you like crazy.

1143
01:36:57,850 --> 01:37:02,050
There's only one place for me to go.

1144
01:37:06,310 --> 01:37:08,460
Can you stay with me forever?

1145
01:37:17,600 --> 01:37:18,600
Nao.

1146
01:37:20,880 --> 01:37:22,360
I like you.

1147
01:37:30,570 --> 01:37:32,370
I love you.

1148
01:37:38,220 --> 01:37:40,570
There may be hard times ahead.

1149
01:37:42,000 --> 01:37:44,370
We might hurt each other again.

1150
01:37:48,340 --> 01:37:52,650
Even so, we are still attracted to each other.

1151
01:37:56,080 --> 01:37:57,800
There is something

1152
01:37:58,820 --> 01:38:00,480
(Cursed in love)
wrong with us.
